## Performance & Optimization
- **Mobile & Responsive Design:**
  - Fully responsive interface using Tailwind CSS breakpoints
  - Mobile-first approach with touch-friendly UI elements
  - Collapsible sidebar for mobile viewing
  - Optimized data tables with horizontal scrolling on small screens
  
- **SEO Optimization:**
  - Metadata configuration using Next.js metadata API
  - Semantic HTML structure for better accessibility
  - Performance optimized with Next.js App Router
  - Server Components for improved initial load times

- **Data Loading & Caching Strategy:**
  - Server Components for initial data fetching
  - Optimistic UI updates for improved user experience
  - Bitcoin price data cached in Supabase tables
  - Interval-based price updates with efficient polling

- **Database Security:**
  - Row-Level Security (RLS) policies on all tables
  - User-specific data access controls
  - Secure authentication flow with Supabase Auth
  - PostgreSQL functions with security definer

- **Privacy Implementation:**
  - No third-party tracking or analytics
  - Minimal personal data collection (email only)
  - No exchange API integration required
  - Client-side CSV processing
 
- **Storage Optimization:**
  - Efficient CSV storage in Supabase Storage
  - File reference tracking in database
  - Automatic cleanup of unused resources
  - Size validation for uploaded files

